Date: Mon, 4 May 2026 20:16:36 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] [d3d11]: Optimize GetMaxFeatureLevel and shader memory
 efficiency

- Decoupled GetMaxFeatureLevel from class instantiation to reduce overhead
- Implemented zero-copy shader bytecode handling in D3D11ShaderConverter
- Added dynamic GPU virtual address bit calculation based on hardware limits
- Improved multisample logic using independent multisampling probes
