Subject: [PATCH 2/2] [d3d11]: Optimize shader creation and VA bits calculation

- Avoid redundant string allocations in CreateIrShader by using

  the raw DxvkShaderHash for cache lookups.

- Fix potential use-after-free by ensuring the converter takes

  ownership of shader bytecode.

- Improve MaxGPUVirtualAddressBits accuracy using physical

  memory properties and bit-scanning instead of log functions.
